description:
Watch our promotional video and share this great event with everyone

 https://youtu.be/hEbzKwOtZ6k 

PyCon Colombia 2023 is the seventh version of the national Python conference in Colombia, This year PyCon Colombia returns with great guests from different countries, who will be happy to share their ideas, experiences and knowledge with all the attendees

Learn more about PyCon Colombia 2023 on our website

https://2023.pycon.co/

There you will find more information about our speakers, talks, organizers and sponsors

Do not forget to follow us on our social networks, so, you will not miss any updates

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pyconcolombia
Twitter: https://twitter.com/pyconcolombia
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/pyconcolombia/
LinkedIn https://www.linkedin.com/company/pycon-colombia/
